### Start provisioning - happy path
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/provisioning
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriberName": "Alice",
  "serviceType": "DATA_5G",
  "simulateActivationFailure": false
}

### Start provisioning - forced failure (compensation flow)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/provisioning
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriberName": "Bob",
  "serviceType": "VOLTE",
  "simulateActivationFailure": true
}

### Get provisioning status (replace {{sagaId}} with the id returned above)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/provisioning/{{sagaId}}

### Health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Prometheus metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus
